snippet.title: I'm 17 and I'm MAKING My Dream Game!
snippet.description:
This is the entire story of how I made my dream game at 17

🔥Pre-order discount + your name in the credits!
❗️You can even get very early access, or put your name on a dungeon tombstone❗️
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/gargantuagames/cavescape-a-multiplayer-strategy-adventure-game

🎮Wishlist Cavescape on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3094540/Cavescape

❤️Join the Gargantua Discord server!
https://discord.gg/FMukgCx8qZ

---Credits---

All the music in this video is from Kalamity music (it's really good)
https://www.youtube.com/@Kalamity_Music

Hollowknight gameplay - C A I O
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1LFoIBE2Nrc
